<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erreur serveur - Energreen</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 50%, #bd2130 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Particules anim√©es en arri√®re-plan */
        .bg-animation {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .particle {
            position: absolute;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 15s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0; }
            50% { opacity: 0.3; }
        }

        /* Container principal */
        .error-container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 35px 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
            animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Ic√¥ne d'erreur */
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 70px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
        }

        /* Code erreur 500 */
        .error-code {
            font-size: 90px;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #e63946);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* Titre */
        .error-title {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        /* Message */
        .error-message {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Conteneur de boutons */
        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Styles de boutons */
        .btn-custom {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .btn-custom:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-primary-custom {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a361c, #2e7d32);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2110, #1b4d1f);
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom {
            background: #6c757d;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom:hover {
            background: #5a6268;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .error-container {
                padding: 40px 25px;
            }

            .error-code {
                font-size: 80px;
            }

            .error-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .button-group {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .btn-custom {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Animation d'arri√®re-plan -->
    <div class="bg-animation">
        <div class="particle" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; left: 10%; animation-delay: 0s;"></div>
        <div class="particle" style="width: 40px; height: 40px; left: 80%; animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
        <div class="particle" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; left: 50%; animation-delay: 4s;"></div>
        <div class="particle" style="width: 35px; height: 35px; left: 30%; animation-delay: 6s;"></div>
        <div class="particle" style="width: 45px; height: 45px; left: 70%; animation-delay: 8s;"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Container d'erreur -->
    <div class="error-container">
        <i class="fas fa-server error-icon"></i>
        <div class="error-code">500</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">Erreur interne du serveur</h1>
        <p class="error-message">
            Oups ! Quelque chose s'est mal pass√© de notre c√¥t√©. üõ†Ô∏è<br>
            Nos √©quipes ont √©t√© notifi√©es et travaillent √† r√©soudre ce probl√®me.<br>
            Veuillez r√©essayer dans quelques instants.
        </p>

        <div class="button-group">
            <button onclick="goBack()" class="btn-custom btn-secondary-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                Retour
            </button>
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-custom btn-primary-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                Tableau de bord
            </a>
        </div>


    </div>

    <script>
        function goBack() {
            if (window.history.length > 1) {
                window.history.back();
            } else {
                window.location.href = '/dashboard';
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
